  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to compare current standing balance assessment methods to a new
      method that measures weight shift during small movements of a sliding platform. It will also
      be used to determine if balance improves with repeated exposure as part of a 4-week training
      program.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
